             was indicted for <rs id="t17911207-40-off220" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17911207-40-off220" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17911207-40-off220" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17911207-40-cd221" type="crimeDate">16th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17911207-40-off220 t17911207-40-cd221"></join> last, 150 lb. weight of raw cotton, value 11 l. and one linen bag, value 1 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17911207-40-victim466" type="victimName">
                     Matthew 
                     Pickford
                  <interp inst="t17911207-40-victim466" type="surname" value="Pickford"></interp>
