                     <interp inst="t17911207-40-person473" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I know the prisoner as a jobbing porter: he is a very honest man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17911207-40-person474">
